snippet.title: KindFolx Adventurer Trailer #2
snippet.description: The Adventurer is a class with a wide variety of tools to keep them alive, guarded, and dishing out damage! The most balanced of the classes, and even able to level up 2 of its starting base cards, the Adventurer's experience gives them more than enough skill to make their way into the heart of KindFolx and challenge Darlocke!
